♪ ...la, la, la ♪

49:07.745 --> 49:08.945
♪ The boys are waiting ♪

49:08.947 --> 49:10.713
♪ My milkshake brings
all the boys to the yard ♪

49:10.715 --> 49:13.115
♪ And they're like,
"It's better than yours" ♪

